ts/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最叻咪鍵盤戰士，哩頭屌澳門人唔俾人上lihkg<br />\n嗰頭派錢就開po葡萄<br />\n真係好撚矛盾"},{"pid":"7a5e135ac3c69b74e05dd17db2e3892c14b58ffe","tid":996343,"uid":52558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:46:25.000Z","msg":"早10年前澳門人一夠18歲就入賭場/廳做<br />\n一邊做一邊進修<br />\n兩公婆做個主任級數年薪已經130萬左右<br />\n就算賭收減弱都買得起樓有餘再養多兩個仔<br />\n賺夠就環遊世界享受生活<br />\n香港文員仔一個月有冇萬八蚊？<br />\n賺到錢嘅咪啲倫敦金嗰啲仆街仔<br />\n成日屌嚟屌去，實際上大部分香港人都慘過做狗"},{"pid":"d97878656535ee9183392d37d577c9cdaa4adb46","tid":996343,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:48:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a7ccd306294afe3a9fcd2e8815820ca1ef6bf2d","tid":996343,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:48:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68040daf4106ff8177a602982b02294a1d1e7e2a","tid":996343,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bb48b1de38b12b32192eda0614847b12e2527fd","tid":996343,"uid":50328,"like":80,"dislike":3,"score":77,"quote":{"pid":"8d2832d6dbf2709c17c1167a11f31937e8b84e91","tid":996343,"uid":41245,"like":20,"dislike":12,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T08:58:58.000Z","msg":"點解要葡萄澳門人？<br />\n要葡萄你唔葡萄個好啲嘅？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:10:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:56:01.000Z","msg":"呢個真，拎葡國護照移民去歐洲，年年派錢慢慢搣，打份牛工都夠過世，香港人仲賤過畜牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9220e0aaf0ae642692fb38160bf475801f43002b","tid":996343,"uid":36543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a71260dda90a6ae1dcedb0c5cb62e2e0ce9440ff","tid":996343,"uid":50328,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:20:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"澳門警察一挑三有冇片睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecf0251e673d2944a26a4154bd45